.SH SUPPORTED FILE TYPES
Over 100 extensions are recognised, including:
.PP
.B Shell:
sh, bash, csh, tcsh, zsh
.br
.B Scripting:
py, pl, pm, rb, php, awk, sed, lua, tcl
.br
.B Web:
js, mjs, jsx, ts, tsx, htm, html, css, json, xml, vue, svelte, graphql
.br
.B Compiled:
c, cpp, cc, cxx, h, hpp, java, go, rs, cs, swift, scala, d
.br
.B Functional:
hs, lhs, erl, hrl, ex, exs, lisp, ml, mli
.br
.B Data/Config:
yaml, yml, ini, conf, cfg, toml, properties, csv, tsv, jsonl, jsonc, proto
.br
.B Markup:
md, markdown, tex, sty
.br
.B Infrastructure:
tf, tfvars, nix, gradle
.br
.B Other:
sql, diff, patch, r, prolog, pascal, fortran, cobol, verilog, vhdl, kotlin,
dart, zig, nim
.
